<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>The Experience - Lumina Cafe</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            lumina: {
              cream: '#fff8f5',
              mint: '#4ade80',
              'mint-dark': '#006d36',
              peach: '#fb923c',
              espresso: '#221a14',
              'espresso-light': '#3d4a3e'
            }
          },
          fontFamily: {
            serif: ['Playfair Display', 'serif'],
            sans: ['Plus Jakarta Sans', 'sans-serif']
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
    h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
    .glass {
      background: rgba(255, 248, 245, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(109, 123, 109, 0.1);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-lumina-cream text-lumina-espresso">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 glass border-b border-lumina-mint/10">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-lumina-mint-dark tracking-tighter">LUMINA</a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-lumina-espresso-light">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-lumina-mint transition-colors">Home</a>
        <a href="/menu" class="hover:text-lumina-mint transition-colors">Menu</a>
        <a href="/reservations" class="hover:text-lumina-mint transition-colors">Reservations</a>
        <a href="/about" class="text-lumina-mint-dark border-b-2 border-lumina-mint pb-1">Experience</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-lumina-mint transition-colors">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a href="/cart" class="relative text-lumina-espresso-light hover:text-lumina-mint transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z"/></svg>
        <% if (cartCount > 0) { %>
          <span class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 bg-lumina-peach text-white text-xs rounded-full h-5 w-5 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow-lg shadow-lumina-peach/40"><%= cartCount %></span>
        <% } %>
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-20">
    <section class="bg-lumina-espresso py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-lumina-mint/10 blur-3xl rounded-full translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
        <p class="text-lumina-mint uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs font-bold mb-6">Sip the Sunshine</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter leading-tight">The Lumina <span class="italic text-lumina-mint">Experience</span></h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-lumina-mint/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full scale-75"></div>
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501339847302-ac426a4a7cbb?w=800&h=1000&fit=crop" alt="Lumina Sanctuary" class="relative z-10 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl transform -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700"/>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-lumina-peach font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-6">Our Philosophy</p>
          <h2 class="text-5xl font-black text-lumina-espresso mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tighter">Where Light <span class="italic text-lumina-mint-dark">Meets</span> Flavor</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-lumina-espresso-light leading-relaxed">
            <p>Lumina was envisioned as more than just a destination for coffee. It's a vibrant sanctuary—a space where the fast-paced urban rhythm slows down to a gentle hum.</p>
            <p>We believe that your morning ritual deserves a backdrop of natural light, organic fluidity, and the highest expression of craft. Every corner of our space is designed to foster inspiration, whether you're a digital nomad seeking focus or an aesthetic seeker chasing the golden hour.</p>
            <p class="font-bold italic text-lumina-mint-dark">"Lumina is the pulse of the community, wrapped in the warmth of a sun-drenched escape."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-lumina-mint/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-lumina-espresso mb-16 tracking-tighter">The <span class="italic text-lumina-mint-dark">Lumina</span> Pillars</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div class="glass p-12 rounded-[3rem] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-lumina-mint/20 rounded-[2rem] flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-8 mx-auto">🍃</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lumina-espresso mb-4">Pure Sourcing</h3>
            <p class="text-lumina-espresso-light text-sm leading-relaxed">We trace every bean to its origin, ensuring regenerative farming practices and direct-trade transparency.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass p-12 rounded-[3rem] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-lumina-peach/20 rounded-[2rem] flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-8 mx-auto">⚡</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lumina-espresso mb-4">Precision Craft</h3>
            <p class="text-lumina-espresso-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Our baristas are masters of extraction, utilizing scientific precision to highlight the vibrant notes of every roast.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass p-12 rounded-[3rem] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-lumina-mint/20 rounded-[2rem] flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-8 mx-auto">☁️</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lumina-espresso mb-4">Urban Oasis</h3>
            <p class="text-lumina-espresso-light text-sm leading-relaxed">A sanctuary for the mind. Comfortable ergonomics, high-speed connectivity, and an atmosphere of calm.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-lumina-espresso text-lumina-cream py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1">
        <h4 class="text-white font-black font-serif text-3xl mb-6 tracking-tighter">LUMINA</h4>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50 max-w-xs">A vibrant sanctuary designed for digital nomads and aesthetic seekers. Sip the sunshine in every cup.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lumina-mint font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-8">Navigate</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm font-medium">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/menu" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Menu</a>
          <a href="/reservations" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Reservations</a>
          <a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Experience</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lumina-peach font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-8">Hours</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-white/70">
          <p>Mon–Fri: 7am – 9pm</p>
          <p>Sat–Sun: 8am – 10pm</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lumina-mint font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-8">Visit</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-white/70">
          <p>42 Elm Street, Downtown</p>
          <p>hello@luminacafe.com</p>
          <p>(555) 123-4567</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 mt-16 pt-10 text-center text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/30">
      &copy; 2026 Lumina Cafe. Crafted for the vibrant sanctuary.
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
